   STAT OF THE WEEK
</P>
<P>
   Since the beginning of the '96 season, free safety Brock Marion
has played in 37 games, all starts, first for Dallas and now Miami.
The six-year pro has earned $4.69 million in that period but has
zero interceptions.
</P>
