<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Nov. 29 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Brad Nelson at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
FBC-USC (Los Angeles) _ USC-Notre Dame game. 5 p.m. PST.
<TEXT>
<P>
   By Scott Wolf. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-MODESTI-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Column from USC-Notre Dame.
</P>
<P>
   By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Column from USC-Notre Dame.
</P>
<P>
   By Karen Crouse. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-USC-SIDE (Los Angeles) _ USC-Notre Dame sidebar.
</P>
<P>
   By Steve Irvine/Long Beach Press-Telegram. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BKC-UCLA-KENTUCKY (Bayamon, Puerto Rico) _ UCLA loses to
Kentucky 66-62 at the Puerto Rico Shootout.
</P>
<P>
