<HEADLINE>
BROWN REFLECTS ON SUCCESSFUL SEASON AT TEXAS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JIMMY BURCH 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
